      "para_id": "Q001492.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , made an eternal thing appear : he built his E-ĝidru , the temple of seven niches ."
    }
